== 製作 ==
2004年，[[夢工廠|夢工廠]]取得亞洲以外《[[攻殼機動隊2_INNOCENCE|攻殼機動隊2 INNOCENCE]]》的發行權<ref>{{cite news | url = http://eiga.com/news/20040302/10/ | script-title = ja:ドリームワークスによる世界配給も決定！「イノセンス」完成会見 | publisher = {{lang|ja|映画.com}} | accessdate =  | date = 2004-03-02 | archive-date = 2017-04-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170407143350/http://eiga.com/news/20040302/10/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，而與[[Production_I.G|Production I.G]]建立良好關係。因此夢工廠跟[[講談社|講談社]]談[[士郎正宗|士郎正宗]]原作權利時，Production I.G充當代理人角色居中協調<ref name=pig>{{cite interview |subject=[[石川光久|石川光久]] |url=http://japanese.engadget.com/2017/03/14/production-i-g/ |title={{lang|ja|「攻殻の実写化、日本発じゃなくて良かった」Production I.G 石川社長インタビュー。『ゴースト・イン・ザ・シェル』製作総指揮が語る真意は}} |publisher=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |interviewer={{lang|ja|砂流恵介}} |language= |date=2017-03-14 |accessdate= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407054834/http://japanese.engadget.com/2017/03/14/production-i-g/ |archivedate=2017-04-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

2008年，夢工廠和[[史蒂芬·史匹柏|史蒂芬·史匹柏]]獲得了漫畫《[[攻殼機動隊|攻殼機動隊]]》的真人改編權。{{link-en|艾維·阿拉德|Avi Arad}}和{{link-en|史蒂芬·保羅|Steven Paul}}後來被證實將擔任監製，由《[[正義悍將|正義悍將]]》的編劇{{link-en|傑米·莫斯|Jamie Moss}}撰寫劇本<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117984029?refCatId=13 | title=DreamWorks to make 'Ghost' in 3-D | publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | accessdate=2011-11-09 | first1=Tatiana | last1=Siegel | first2=Michael | last2=Fleming | date=2008-04-14 | archive-date=2012-10-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020141904/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117984029?refCatId=13 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年10月，宣布《[[隔離島|隔離島]]》的編劇{{link-en|萊塔·卡羅格里迪斯|Laeta Kalogridis}}取代了莫斯<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118010309?refCatId=13 | title = Kalogridis to adapt 'Ghost in the Shell' | publisher = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | accessdate = 2011-11-09 | first = Tatiana | last = Siegel | date = 2009-10-22 | archive-date = 2011-08-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110805053937/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118010309?refCatId=13 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2010年，艾維·阿拉德就任美國Production I.G.,LLC董事長<ref>{{cite press release | url = http://eir.eol.co.jp/EIR/View.aspx?cat=tdnet&sid=825817 | script-title = ja:Production I.G.,LLC の会長にアヴィ・アラッド氏就任のお知らせ | publisher = {{lang|ja|株式会社IGポート}} | accessdate =  | date = 2010-08-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160417060614/http://eir.eol.co.jp/EIR/View.aspx?cat=tdnet&sid=825817 | archive-date = 2016-04-17 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，大幅縮短美日之間溝通的距離<ref>{{cite news | author = 壬生智裕 | url = http://www.cinematoday.jp/page/N0090774 | script-title = ja:ハリウッド版「攻殻機動隊」称賛の理由は Production I.G石川社長が語る | publisher = {{lang|ja|シネマトゥデイ}} | accessdate =  | date = 2017-04-06 | archive-date = 2017-04-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170407055533/http://www.cinematoday.jp/page/N0090774 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。 

