sdate=2015-11-11|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2015-11-10|archive-date=2015-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151113000115/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/pilou-asbaek-scarlett-johansson-ghost-in-the-shell-1201637556/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年11月19日，據報導，[[山姆·萊利|山姆·萊利]]正在會談加入本片，飾演一名危險極端罪犯的反派角色<ref name=RileyTalks>{{cite news|last1=Jaafar|first1=Ali|title=Sam Riley In Talks For ‘Ghost In The Shell’ Opposite Scarlett Johansson|url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/sam-riley-in-talks-ghost-in-the-shell-scarlett-johansson-dreamworks-paramount-lily-james-brie-larson-1201630113/|accessdate=2015-11-28|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2015-11-19|archive-date=2015-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123100413/http://deadline.com/2015/11/sam-riley-in-talks-ghost-in-the-shell-scarlett-johansson-dreamworks-paramount-lily-james-brie-larson-1201630113/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但於2016年2月4日，據報導，[[麥可·彼特|麥可·彼特]]才是萊利的角色飾演者<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/ghost-in-the-shell-michael-pitt-scarlett-johansson-1201697737/|title=Michael Pitt to Play Villain in Scarlett Johansson’s ‘Ghost in the Shell’|publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|last=Kroll|first=Justin|date=2016-02-04|accessdate=2016-02-05|archive-date=2016-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206080703/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/ghost-in-the-shell-michael-pitt-scarlett-johansson-1201697737/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年3月3日，據[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]網站報導，日本演員[[北野武|北野武]]將飾演公安9課部長[[公安9課#荒卷大輔|荒卷大輔]]，[[Production_I.G|Production I.G]]社長[[石川光久|石川光久]]擔任[[執行製作人|執行製作人]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.thewrap.com/scarlett-johanssons-ghost-in-the-shell-casts-its-first-japanese-actor/ | title=Scarlett Johansson’s ‘Ghost in the Shell’ Casts Its First Japanese Actor | publisher=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]] | date=2016-03-02 | accessdate=2016-03-03 | last=Snider | first=Jeff | archive-date=2016-03-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305094721/http://www.thewrap.com/scarlett-johanssons-ghost-in-the-shell-casts-its-first-japanese-actor/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年4月，演員[[茱麗葉·畢諾許|茱麗葉·畢諾許]]、[[桃井薰|桃井薰]]和[[黃經漢|黃經漢]]也加入了電影<ref name="#1"/>。2016年5月，宣布[[福島莉拉|福島莉拉]]加入演出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/wolverine-actress-rila-fukushima-joins-896857|title='Wolverine' Actress Rila Fukushima Joins Scarlett Johansson in 'Ghost in the Shell' (Exclusive)|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|last2=Galuppo|first2=Mia|date=2016-05-25|accessdate=2016-05-27|archive-date=2016-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160526130133/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/wolverine-actress-rila-fukushima-joins-896857|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

