== 選角爭議 ==
由身為白人的史嘉蕾·喬韓森主演草薙素子而在欧美地区引起了爭議，尤其喜愛日本原作的愛好者<ref>{{cite web|last=Brown|first=Tracey|title=‘Ghost in the Shell’: Scarlett Johansson casting called ‘whitewashing’|url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/ghost-in-the-shell-scarlett-johansson-casting-a-blow-to-diversity/|accessdate=2016-04-14|work=Hero Complex|date=2015-01-10|archive-date=2016-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160418204925/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/ghost-in-the-shell-scarlett-johansson-casting-a-blow-to-diversity/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="child">{{cite news | last=Child | first=Ben | url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/jan/16/dreamworks-scarlett-johansson-ghost-in-the-shell-whitewashing | title=DreamWorks accused of 'whitewashing' Ghost in the Shell by casting Scarlett Johansson | work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | date=2015-01-16 | accessdate=2016-04-14 | archive-date=2016-04-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417210621/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/jan/16/dreamworks-scarlett-johansson-ghost-in-the-shell-whitewashing | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#2">{{cite web | last=Fuster | first=Jeremy | url=http://www.thewrap.com/ghost-in-the-shell-fans-not-happy-about-whitewashed-american-remake/ | title=‘Ghost In The Shell’ Fans Not Happy About ‘Whitewashed’ American Remake | work=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]] | date=2016-04-14 | accessdate=2016-04-14 | archive-date=2016-04-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417145613/http://www.thewrap.com/ghost-in-the-shell-fans-not-happy-about-whitewashed-american-remake/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last=Calvario | first=Liz | url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/scarlett-johansson-ghost-in-the-shell-photo-first-20160414 | title=Scarlett Johansson Becomes Major Motoko Kusanagi in 'Ghost In The Shell' First Look | work=IndieWire | date= | accessdate=2016-04-14 | archive-date=2016-04-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415082703/http://www.indiewire.com/article/scarlett-johansson-ghost-in-the-shell-photo-first-20160414 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last=Dish | first=Daily | url=http://blog.chron.com/celebritybuzz/2016/04/mulan-star-upset-with-scarlett-johansson-casting-in-classic-japanese-manga-film/ | title='Mulan' star upset with Scarlett Johansson casting in classic Japanese Manga film | work=Chron.com ([[赫斯特国际集团|Hearst Newspapers]]) | date=2016-04-15 | accessdate= | archive-date=2016-04-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417233732/http://blog.chron.com/celebritybuzz/2016/04/mulan-star-upset-with-scarlett-johansson-casting-in-classic-japanese-manga-film/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last=Sampson | first=Mike | url=http://screencrush.com/ghost-in-the-shell-whitewashing-scarlett-johnasson-vfx | title=Exclusive: 'Ghost in the Shell' Producers Reportedly Tested Visual Effects That Would Make White Actors Appear Asian | work=ScreenCrush | date=2016-04-15 | accessdate= | archive-date=2016-04-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417121352/http://screencrush.com/ghost-in-the-shell-whitewashing-scarlett-johnasson-vfx/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。有些愛好者認為如果改編主角的日本人設定或名字以配合電影可能較好<ref name="#2"/>。據傳，派拉蒙打算以CGI技術來讓史嘉蕾·喬韓森看起來像亞洲人<ref>{{cite web | last=Sampson | first=Mike | url=http://screencrush.com/ghost-in-the-shell-whitewashing-scarlett-johnasson-vfx/ | title=Exclusive: ‘Ghost in the Shell’ Producers Reportedly Tested Visual Effects That Would Make White Actors Appear Asian | work=[[ScreenCrush|ScreenCrush]] | date=2016-04-14 | accessdate=2016-04-19 | archive-date=2016-04-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160419044535/http://screencrush.com/ghost-in-the-shell-whitewashing-scarlett-johnasson-vfx/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。派拉蒙澄清，這CGI技術只是一個短暫的測試，並不影響史嘉蕾·喬韓森的外貌<ref name="A-list">{{cite web|last=Child|first=Ben|title=Max Landis: there are ‘no A-list female Asian celebrities’ who could have taken Scarlett Johansson’s Ghost in a Shell role|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/apr/18/max-landis-denies-defence-of-scarlett-johansson-ghost-in-the-shell|accessdate=2016-04-18|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=2016-04-18|archive-date=2016-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160418120523/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/apr/18/max-landis-denies-defence-of-scarlett-johansson-ghost-in-the-shell|dead-url=no}}</ref>。部分愛好者和業內人士認為此爭議的問題是他們只在意電影票房，現在的好萊塢擔心非白人演員所帶來的利益會比白人還少<ref name="A-list" />。

相反地，日本愛好者對好萊塢所引起的爭議感到訝異，多數認為讓白人史嘉蕾·喬韓森來演的主意並不差<ref name="thr">{{cite web | last=Blair | first=Gavin J. | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/scarlett-johansson-ghost-shell-japanese-885462 | title=Scarlett Johansson in 'Ghost in the Shell': Japanese Industry, Fans Surprised by "Whitewashing" Outrage | work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date=2016-04-19 | accessdate=2016-04-20 | archive-date=2016-04-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420065517/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/scarlett-johansson-ghost-shell-japanese-885462 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

監製{{link-en|史蒂芬·保羅|Steven Paul}}解釋女主角的名字只有「少校」（The Major）二字，儘管取材自草薙素子；並聲稱電影是設定成「國際性的世界」，在片中會有各種形形色色的民族，如日本人、中國人、英國人和美國人{{r|theMajor}}。但電影尾聲卻證實「少校」原名「Motoko Kusanagi」（草薙素子）。

== 發行 ==
2015年4月29日，迪士尼公司宣布電影的上映日為2017年3月31日<ref>{{cite news|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|title=Disney Moves ‘Ghost In The Shell’ Up Two Weeks|url=http://deadline.com/2015/04/disney-moves-ghost-in-the-shell-to-march-31-2017-1201418351/|accessdate=2015-04-30|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2015-04-29|archive-date=2015-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150502214515/http://deadline.com/2015/04/disney-moves-ghost-in-the-shell-to-march-31-2017-1201418351/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年1月25日，迪士尼將發行權讓出，夢工廠改和[[環球影業|環球影業]]合作，由環球影業負責美國的發行權；後來，證實[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]成為了在全球發行的片商<ref>{{cite news|last=Romano|first=Nick|title=Girl on the Train, Ghost in the Shell Release Dates Dropped|url=http://collider.com/the-girl-on-the-train-ghost-in-the-shell-disney-release-dates-dropped/|accessdate=2016-01-26|work=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|date=2016-01-25|archive-date=2016-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160129045131/http://collider.com/the-girl-on-the-train-ghost-in-the-shell-disney-release-dates-dropped/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後迪士尼將發行權完全轉至派拉蒙影業，並保留了2017年3月31日的上映日<ref name=DisToPar>{{cite news|last1=Stedman|first1=Alex|title='Ghost in the Shell' Moves to Paramount From Disney|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/ghost-in-the-shell-release-date-paramount-disney-1201688478/|accessdate=2016-01-26|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2016-01-25|archive-date=2016-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127004506/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/ghost-in-the-shell-release-date-paramount-disney-1201688478/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===評價===
《攻殼機動隊》獲得了褒貶不一的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於273條評論，新鮮度43%，平均得分5.51／10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ghost_in_the_shell_2017 |title=Ghost in the Shell (2017) |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2017-03-28 |archive-date=2017-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171230090249/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ghost_in_the_shell_2017/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，獲得了52分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/ghost-in-the-shell-2017 |title=Ghost in the Shell reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2017-03-28 |archive-date=2019-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190208205238/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/ghost-in-the-shell-2017 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的反應在A+至F間落於「B」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |accessdate=2017-03-30 |archive-date=2019-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210223808/https://m.cinemascore.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。多數影評人認為電影有著炫目的特效和視覺效果，而喬韓森的演出也令人信服，但仍缺少原作經典的迷人要素。

=== 票房 ===
在美國和加拿大，《攻殼機動隊》與《[[寶貝老闆|寶貝老闆]]》、《[[園長夫人：動物園的奇蹟|園長夫人：動物園的奇蹟]]》共同上映及競爭，估計於首週末能從三千四百四十間戲院中獲得2500萬美元的票房<ref name=preview>{{cite web |last=Fuster |first=Jeremy |url=http://www.thewrap.com/boss-baby-and-ghost-in-the-shell-to-take-on-beauty-and-the-beast-this-weekend/ |title='Boss Baby,' 'Ghost in the Shell' to Battle 'Beauty and the Beast' This Weekend |publisher=The Wrap |date=2017-03-27 |accessdate=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2017-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170401022741/http://www.thewrap.com/boss-baby-and-ghost-in-the-shell-to-take-on-beauty-and-the-beast-this-weekend/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但結果首週末僅獲得1900萬美元的票房，位居當週票房排名第三，該成績低於預期，甚至達不到首周末海外票房的一半<ref>{{cite web |author=Anthony D'Alessandro |url=http://deadline.com/2017/03/ghost-in-the-shell-scarlett-johansson-boss-baby-beauty-and-the-beast-weekend-box-office-1202056616/ |title=Boss Baby’ Bullies ‘Beast’ With $50M+ Opening; ‘Ghost’ Shell-Shocked With Low $18.6M |publisher=Deadline |accessdate=2017-04-02 |archive-date=2017-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170401142137/http://deadline.com/2017/03/ghost-in-the-shell-scarlett-johansson-boss-baby-beauty-and-the-beast-weekend-box-office-1202056616/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。


